       <div class="ui-portlet-content"> 
        <h2 class="Content-title">【达斡尔族抗日斗争大事记】</h2> 
        <div class="Content-info">
          2015-10-05 19:19 &nbsp;&nbsp; 
         <a href="/wxes/16628">鄂温克旗彩虹之家</a> &nbsp;&nbsp; 
        </div> 
        <div class="Content-body"> 
         <!-- <div class="ui-share">
		    	<div class="btn btn-default"><a href="javasctipt:void(0);" onclick="return addtofavor('Article','591353');">分享</a></div>
		    	<div class="ui-share-num"><span class="ui-stats-num" id="Stats-Article-591353-favor_nums">0</span></div>
		    </div> --> 
         <p><img data-type="gif" src="http://rdn.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9mRnExOTJkMnNuaWFlcFhyZUZUbldjbWVEMU5VaWJRVXZ6aWJ6NWxUcGhpYWgwTTRXa0hlY2FkNFVVaWMySzJWVVNvQnJJRVNOa1VGWkhscG9icWc4Q1FjTXVnLzA/d3hfZm10PWdpZg==" data-ratio="0.11834319526627218" data-w="507" /><br /></p>
         <section class="135editor" data-id="44390" style="">
          <section data-bcless="darken" style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(8, 154, 228); text-align: center; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 1px 0px, rgb(197, 200, 204) 0px 2px 0px, rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px, rgb(197, 200, 204) 0px 4px 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 25px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(89, 195, 249); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(89, 195, 249); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <section data-width="14px" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(173, 173, 173); height: 14px; width: 14px; border-top-left-radius: 7px; border-top-right-radius: 7px; border-bottom-right-radius: 7px; border-bottom-left-radius: 7px;">
             <section data-width="14px" style="margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); height: 14px; width: 14px; border-top-left-radius: 7px; border-top-right-radius: 7px; border-bottom-right-radius: 7px; border-bottom-left-radius: 7px;">
              <br />
             </section>
             <section data-width="8px" style="margin: -37px 0px 0px 2px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 8px; height: 30px; border: 1px solid rgb(202, 202, 202); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;">
              <br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" />
              <br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" />
             </section>
             <p><span style="font-size: 16px; text-align: left; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br /></span></p>
             <p><span style="font-size: 16px; text-align: left; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br /></span></p>
             <p><br /></p>
            </section>
           </section>
           <section class="135brush" style="margin: 40px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <p style="white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;">前言：</span></strong><br style="white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /> 前不久，在微信群中听一些族人说起达斡尔族在抗战时期没什么表现、作用不大时，我深感错愕。觉得有必要以正视听，遂将自己参加内蒙古达斡尔学会2015年9月10日召开的纪念达斡尔族抗战70周年座谈会所写文章中的一节转贴于此，一为向达斡尔族牺牲奋斗的老前辈追悼和致敬。二为尊重历史，杜绝误导，做一个宣传。三是欢迎各位继续搜集补充。</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />沃泽明 2015年9月30日</span></p>
           </section>
          </section>
          <section data-width="0px" style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
         </section>
         <p style=""><br /></p>
         <p>从1931年9.18事变到1945年8月15日抗日战争彻底胜利，达斡尔族人民经历了艰苦卓绝的14年抗日斗争。以下按年份选择一些代表性的片断，展示一下达斡尔族人民抗战的足迹和斗争的历程，以管中窥豹的方式陈列于此：<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />1931年当张学良在日寇发动9.18后宣布放弃东三省时，达斡尔族著名领袖、内蒙古人民革命党代理委员长郭道甫庄重宣告：“死也不做日本的奴隶，坚决同日本帝国主义抗战到底”。在马占山指挥的抗击日寇入侵的江桥战役中，齐齐哈尔达斡尔族人民纷纷组织担架队、慰劳队，救助伤员和慰问将士，全力支持了全国第一场抗日之战。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.2583826429980276" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/49dIH77fkrqwpC5rFub.hJXs6wgVKhXo7iazFrxQpsk!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=WALyAgAAAAAFAIk!&amp;su=0199305521&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />内蒙古人民革命党代理委员长郭道甫</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.8362919132149902" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://b303.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V11TVWL12xhB1H/Zc9WIEBuBktofhPv*yanelYQwCIPWA3ouEYe69c1LGw%21/b/YfNrqbT6bwAAYmjipLSTbgAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=kQAKAQAAAAADA7w%21&amp;su=0241605889&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.6982248520710059" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://b303.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V11TVWL12xhB1H/UVJSLF*C3Gay0ckmi1QP4DnYLQ5CYOdqFRAXxMdze9k%21/b/YQlpprR.bwAAYpS1m7SybwAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=kAEXAQAAAAADA6E%21&amp;su=0142224673&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1932年当日本扶植的伪满洲国成立时，齐齐哈尔敖宝屯达斡尔族以鄂寿喜为代表的一批青年踊跃参加了抗日义勇军。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7652859960552268" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/QmENGjJpsqDmxloEJToZkiEd6iO1YPSG3ngn2g4KEX0!/b/dHIAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=IAHcAAAAAAABANo!&amp;su=0229301985&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1933年当蒋介石国民政府与日本签订丧权卖国的《塘沽协定》时，达斡尔族末代皇后郭布罗.婉容因再一次逃离伪满洲国而遭严厉监控。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.52465483234714" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/xUsSzHROInX2Lod2qtyburENWmP.N3Ll47UrM8xT*uk!/b/dHMAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=aAEkAgAAAAAFAGw!&amp;su=0222492865&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.4299802761341223" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/1DFoILjfOORuGVHQ4zSJpbaHzfCobAc4NwtOwLBzb24!/b/dGMBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QwHNAQAAAAAFAK0!&amp;su=019487809&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.883629191321499" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/6L9bGk49inkQ3wbsCl6aAFAaMb4TkKtSheQEL4rivkY!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=kAFhAQAAAAABANY!&amp;su=024462081&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1934年中华苏维埃共和国政府和革命军事委员会发表《为中国工农红军北上抗日宣言》时，在伪兴安省警备军中任军官的达斡尔族金寿平宣布战场起义，加入了赵尚志领导的东北抗日游击队哈东支队。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.6765285996055227" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/mI1SavoJgGt9l9hIhd*a5Manr1htbzxi3MSyN*SmQ.g!/b/dHIAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=SwKMAQAAAAABAOM!&amp;su=056911409&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1935年中国共产党发表《为抗日救国告全体同胞书》即《八一宣言》时，讷河县达斡尔族农民郭庆海等人毅然将每个人全部口粮送给了抗日联军第三军第六师，随即加入了抗联。<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />1936年北平爆发抗日救亡的“一二.九”学生运动时，达斡尔族中国共产党党员金寿鹏在齐齐哈尔日本陆军监狱英勇就义；达斡尔族上层爱国人士凌升、华林泰、福龄、春德等四人被日本关东军以“通苏、通蒙、反满抗日罪”杀害。<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />凌升</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.205128205128205" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://b307.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V11TVWL12xhB1H/vVwY72yT*vhrKlitWwH6XeA254SBeWkFNNkxl*xo8nA!/b/YSSfAredJwAAYmE8B7eeKAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AFaAgAAAAABBI4!&amp;su=0268231409&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />华林泰</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.3353057199211045" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://b301.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V11TVWL12xhB1H/Y6cgyJPdJjNh3Xl9sil8ZA8s*yeVwAXXiVymySd5IAk!/b/Yb6nc7MGgAAAYkCSbbOFfwAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AGbAgAAAAABBE8!&amp;su=0101825489&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>福龄</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.370808678500986" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/ZWlrUfXzJDIL2um3sOgnawPbuw*cZPzjo0TiHODI8FU!/b/dHIAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=oAE6AgAAAAABAL4!&amp;su=0155333569&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>春德</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.358974358974359" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/bWxRc.DD2RKijeeSm7u08r*nWUMIEbDUyQoyy4ZmAlk%21/b/dGMBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=oAE1AgAAAAABALE%21&amp;su=0167819377&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.455621301775148" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/SpOlAdKA68NRTpRv96a2QVPWw.Dzl*PpbBA3d7ebS7A%21/b/dGEBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=LAG0AQAAAAABAL8%21&amp;su=0135729969&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1937年七七卢沟桥事变日本发动全面侵华战争时，达斡尔族共产国际情报员海瑞（女）由内蒙古转入北平开展日军情报搜集工作。<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />达斡尔族女情报员晓云</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.1637080867850098" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/L3jIJ7WsKGJrFBkMzWuWHp2HHdBr9z9Ex1L6Yr7tJ04!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AFFAgAAAAABAJU!&amp;su=048541073&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1938年当国民党副总裁汪精卫在河内公开向日本投降时，海瑞情报组和呼伦贝尔达斡尔秘密情报组正分头在北平、海拉尔、沈阳、长春等地，潜入敌营、伪皇宫和日军军事要塞，为共产国际反法西斯战线搜集日本军事情报。<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />1939年当苏联与日本在中蒙边境爆发诺门罕大战时，呼伦贝尔达斡尔秘密情报组向苏军总指挥朱可夫提供了日军兵力配置的大量精准情报，使苏军大获全胜，日本也因此改北上侵苏为南下攻美，扭转了二战发展格局。情报组负责人达斡尔族英雄额尔登毕力格因此还获得了苏联战斗红旗勋章、苏联对日作战胜利奖章、苏联诺门罕战争胜利奖章，并被授予苏联国家英雄称号。同年中共北满省委在讷河成立中共讷河县委，并派遣东北抗联西北远征军进入莫旗，领导讷河、莫旗等达斡尔族地区的抗日斗争。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/BDCOd8fMkPpMRGvKVizsfvyZ5u6OTS8nhzofCkySXwo!/b/dGMBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AF3AQAAAAABAKQ!&amp;su=0148944417&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://rdn.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9mRnExOTJkMnNuaHgzcGFYRXp0VmRPdEdHRXJ2elNuS1kySlRIcm5BQlZ2R3hlWlFiSXJlZ3JINjRCSzNwcFV5d1J0aGY0bTRwWk9RWGJHdzlpYng0cWcvMD93eF9mbXQ9anBlZw==" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.5798816568047337" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/T5IsNGyxyJw0KNvoVc5UfO*0wEJXSe0q7cSLXV1ku2I!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AEhAQAAAAAFAPY!&amp;su=0216789873&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.6627218934911243" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/*M.T8pgjfWUaq*2DJajwPUGEp*bi8*BqJB55ypeDh6Y!/b/dGQBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=xQEsAQAAAAAFAMo!&amp;su=037395393&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />【乌嫩库齐补充】奈勒尔图（1904－1956)，达斡尔族，郭布勒哈拉，又名郭文贵，南屯人。1924年被苏联人色登伊西招幕为远东军情报人员，由此开始他长达20余年苏联地下情报人员的生涯。后与哈斯巴特尔一起组建了一支30多人参加的情报网，在茫茫草原广泛搜集日伪军事战略计划、军事设施、道路桥梁、军警分布及日伪军警特宪等方面的情况。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.1893491124260356" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/Re9oe6KKd2VAsr6*emcBvfiEgUWr3xejVI.pD8k2QYg%21/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AFSAgAAAAABAII%21&amp;su=0185801953&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />达斡尔族抗日英雄哈斯巴特尔与妻子撤尔普乐玛的合影</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.309664694280079" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://b301.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V11TVWL12xhB1H/uaHovRMtP18TuwlP8A5WkNbFJotgLN0L9.FwmTEhDtM%21/b/YVo3dbMFgAAAYgkbb7PtfgAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AGOAgAAAAABBFo%21&amp;su=010608241&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />达斡尔族英雄额尔登毕力格</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="1.5463510848126232" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://rdn.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9mRnExOTJkMnNuaHgzcGFYRXp0VmRPdEdHRXJ2elNuS3dFTmg4MWljd1hMc2hpYkJuOVRTTE5Da0VTVUpyWXRKY1ZYSE5GWWJuTGxpYnhYa21QQkJEMEx2QS8wP3d4X2ZtdD1qcGVn" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>这是他获得的：<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />苏联战斗红旗勋章、<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />苏联对日作战胜利奖章、<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />苏联诺门罕战争胜利奖章、<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />苏联国家英雄称号证书</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.6627218934911243" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/ZLk*KqXVM3uGh5bz3CHZngrlC7yimczKpzhhUcOPVr4%21/b/dGQBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=TAKGAQAAAAAFAOo%21&amp;su=0249219025&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.5069033530571991" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/AsdtmUrT7kvcJmD51FgsWOawJ*4YPYtR27RIl1bKHdI%21/b/dGUAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=CAIOAwAAAAAFACQ%21&amp;su=051039905&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.6627218934911243" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/LQzhH2TnPPWjJG3WGtpUGwDIJ.a6bQ6T5*0wf9H1EhU!/b/dGMBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=sALIAQAAAAAFAFg!&amp;su=0256480497&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1940年当八路军发动对日军百团大战时，东北抗联达斡尔族战士、中共党员郭刚在破袭北兴镇的战斗中击毙敌军机枪手，并为掩护三支队参谋长身重十余颗子弹，壮烈牺牲。<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />【乌嫩库齐补充】阿拉马斯，达斡尔族，16岁参加八路军打击日寇。后来由于种种原因留在了蒙古国。曾任中蒙大使馆馆长。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/LbcReu2wE9m9Zvce7jzFXahV0xmD8Rrl7fdY6MoUwAQ!/b/dHMAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=VAOAAgAAAAAFAPY!&amp;su=071762913&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/khLhHqGvNiQoNzgSt22a3o6VSHSagYFsMnhWJO*TE14!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=VAOAAgAAAAAFAPY!&amp;su=0149326641&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1941年当国民党发动破坏抗战的“皖南事变”时，巴彦旗郭恩屯和卡布楚屯的达斡尔族群众为王明贵率领的抗联部队支援了30多匹战马和一批粮食及防寒衣服鞋帽等，缓解了抗联极端的困难。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/YD4t.fgcN9eWjFAZDopfqtWw4cJifMQzYW96MPTZtsE!/b/dGUAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QAHwAAAAAAABAJY!&amp;su=029511345&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/Lg5no1Z1KR3jLPqpVGSEUB9jv62NZOQ.XHh7aDeGDUs%21/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QAHwAAAAAAABAJY%21&amp;su=0200053377&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/aGZI2NXdCVQsvh36kTRTj2XS9F1TU0SBDMVK56boFKY!/b/dGoAAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QAHwAAAAAAABAJY!&amp;su=0252793201&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/FsVquWhnv3o6yGzRXsNtio46lJxdwB2Z7FufjqjvzvY!/b/dGMBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QAHwAAAAAAABAJY!&amp;su=084335857&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/mjZIg8xnQG2pDLGHvI9kD35KRv*0JCWQgZ47hmca6Uc!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QAHwAAAAAAABAJY!&amp;su=0130527281&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1942年当日军加紧对华北抗日根据地进行残酷“大扫荡”时，为了保护受伤的抗联战士，莫力达瓦旗郭尼、阿尔哈浅屯达斡尔族群众甘冒被日伪军杀戮的危险，将抗联教导队一位受伤的班长胡庆荣秘密保护在敖销诺和孟能阳两家，直到日本投降这位班长才安全归队。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7514792899408284" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/cW.rCzEVeaTk742po5ikcsBnGF8Xecb4c*j3qfdHcog%21/b/dGQBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=QAHwAAAAAAABAJY%21&amp;su=0217675729&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-type="png" data-ratio="0.571992110453649" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://rdn.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9mRnExOTJkMnNuaHgzcGFYRXp0VmRPdEdHRXJ2elNuS2ljd3dpY1hQMUNpYm83VHhHYzJZNWljaWJMMkN5VWgzVDlTUEtQbnpaZzZzOEpTRmxWbzV6UDVqUklRLzA/d3hfZm10PXBuZw==" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1943年当中、美、英三国发表《开罗宣言》时，南屯达斡尔族的抗日英雄苏和巴特尔在日军追捕时将最后一颗子弹射向了自己。共产国际达斡尔族情报员孟江元与中共新疆领导人陈潭秋、毛泽民等人在新疆一同被敌人杀害。 <br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />苏和巴特尔 (1910～l943)，别名郭海涛，达斡尔族，郭布勒哈拉，索伦翼镶黄旗(今鄂温克旗)人。在乌兰乌德学习俄语。一年后，以优秀成绩选入苏联红军坦克学校。毕业后分配在苏联远东军区坦克部队任职。回国后先后5次搜集到极有价值的日伪军事情报。1943年，苏和巴特尔不慎被特务发现，他骑上光背马，跳入特尼河芦苇丛里，边射击边嚼碎情报资料，不幸中弹负伤，用最后一颗子弹自尽殉国。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="1.2998027613412229" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/OBC3xJJyqlnzzgUbW1JlkPz626.Jc4OMwNR1EN8IlhQ!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=9AGJAgAAAAABAFk!&amp;su=0147589793&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>1944年当八路军开辟河南抗日根据地时，共产国际达斡尔族女情报员海瑞在日军特务的包围中英勇就义。<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />1945年8月9号当中国共产党主席毛泽东发表《对日寇的最后一战》，号召中国人民一切抗日力量举行全国规模反攻时，8月10日，伪兴安军第十军达斡尔族中将司令官郭文林在锡尼河举行战场起义，将5名中校和5名少校在内的100余名日军官兵全部歼灭后，随带部队向苏联红军投诚。8月11日，齐齐哈尔籍达斡尔族连长王海山、上尉教官鄂秀峰等人指挥伪满兴安省陆军军官学校8个连600多人击毙日军10余名校尉级军官，在乌兰浩特葛根庙举行了武装起义。5月2日在苏联红军攻克德国柏林的战斗中，达斡尔族坦克兵少尉色尔古楞英勇杀敌，勇猛冲锋，最后壮烈牺牲。</p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-ratio="0.7593688362919132" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V11TVWL13LeABb/G82xHd04M2gZwksVBZYG8pBXa1Wohab5Bnk.URh6TDw!/b/dGUBAAAAAAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=zAFdAQAAAAABALY!&amp;su=0222869825&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-0" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p><img style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16px; display: block; width: 1243px; background-size: cover; -webkit-background-clip: padding-box; background-clip: padding-box; box-sizing: border-box; min-width: 50px; min-height: 20px; background-position: 50% 50%;" data-type="png" data-ratio="1.4536489151873768" data-w="507" class="lazy" data-src="http://rdn.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9mRnExOTJkMnNuaHgzcGFYRXp0VmRPdEdHRXJ2elNuS1VRRnR2ZTBBSGlhaG4zSUx1bnVmbU9zMnh5MGlidDkwWGljZVhGTkM5NmI4V1AyeURTYUdiNXpmQS8wP3d4X2ZtdD1wbmc=" /></p>
         <p><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" /></p>
         <p>至此，在十四年抗日战争的历程中，达斡尔族虽处沦陷区，却涌现出了一批批支援抗战的普通民众，产生了一个个参加战斗的抗联战士，出现了一个个壮烈牺牲的英雄，留下了一串串带血的足迹，为消灭日本法西斯，为夺取抗日战争和世界反法西斯战争的伟大胜利，为中华民族的解放，做出了达斡尔族人民的伟大贡献。 <br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" />引自沃泽明《论达斡尔族在抗日战争中的历史贡献》 第六节<br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);" /><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">来源：<span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">乌嫩库齐QQ空间日志</span></span></p>
         <p>
